data.description: Step into this charming, cozy home, designed with your comfort in mind. Inside, you'll find four spacious bedrooms and two full baths for your family's convenience. We've made some eco-friendly upgrades to keep your energy bills low, including modern double-pane windows and an impressive 8.6KWP solar panel system, complete with a 10kw battery backup to ensure you always have power when you need it. We've also taken care of the essentials, like an encapsulated crawl space with a dehumidifier, a brand-new HVAC system with updated ductwork (installed in 2020), a water heater upgraded in 2021, and shiny new range and dishwasher appliances from 2023. And for those of you with electric cars, we've even included a Clipper Electric Car Charger in the garage. Solar panels are already paid for. Welcome to your new energy-efficient haven!
